data.description:
Located in the heart of Aurora, Colorado, this property at 3714 S Andes Way offers a layout with 5 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, this home provides ample space for families of all sizes.

As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a bright and airy living area, complete with large windows that allow natural light. The  kitchen features granite countertops, and plenty of storage for all your cooking essentials.

The master bedroom comes with an en-suite bathroom and a walk-in closet. The remaining bedrooms are generously sized and perfect for children, guests, or home office space.

Outside, the backyard is a private oasis, ideal for entertaining or simply relaxing on a sunny day. With easy access to parks, schools, shopping, and dining options, this home offers convenience and comfort in a desirable Aurora neighborhood.

Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this beautiful property your own. Schedule a showing today and experience the charm of 3714 S Andes Way for yourself!
